snippet.title: DigDigDrill Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
DigDigDirll is a ground mining,treasure collecting game. 
Dig freely for minerals and treasures. Use the collecting resources to forge your original drills! 
Are you ready to spend your time on grinding tasks and a hack-and-slash style combat system?

Steam store page:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2916770
